window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>She's off limits and he can't resist...</i></p> <p>Three years ago my wolf found my fated mate, and she was my best friend's little sister.</p> <p>He's no longer my friend, and she's off limits. Is it any wonder everyone thinks I'm a dick?</p> <p>Now, I'm the star player for the Bay State U Dire Wolves and I've told myself I don't have or need a mate. Fate can go fuck itself.</p> <p>Until Addy walks into my life. I'm the hot shot of the Dire Wolves football team, but when I take the shot with my best friend's little sister, the beast inside has more on his mind than scoring.</p>"; 
